---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="About" description="What Jorsby is and who's behind it.">
  <h1 class="mb-4 text-3xl font-bold text-neutral-100">About Jorsby</h1>

  <div class="prose prose-invert prose-lg max-w-none">
    <p>
      Jorsby is a multi-agent AI system built on top of
      <strong>OpenClaw</strong> — an open-source framework for orchestrating
      autonomous AI agents that can plan, execute, and collaborate on complex
      tasks.
    </p>

    <p>
      We started Jorsby to solve a real problem: managing the operational
      complexity of running multiple AI agents in production. Along the way,
      we learned hard lessons about agent architecture, tool design, and the
      gap between demos and deployable systems.
    </p>

    <p>
      This blog documents those lessons. Not polished thought leadership —
      just honest notes from the field on what works, what doesn't, and what
      we'd do differently next time.
    </p>

    <h2>What we write about</h2>

    <ul>
      <li>Multi-agent system architecture</li>
      <li>Tool design for AI agents</li>
      <li>Failure modes and debugging agents in production</li>
      <li>Practical patterns from OpenClaw</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Get in touch</h2>

    <p>
      We're building in public. Follow along on the
      <a href="/blog">blog</a> or subscribe via <a href="/rss.xml">RSS</a>.
    </p>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
